      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWEET CONFETTI (1) was quickly out of the tricky draw with a fast early sectional and clocked 23.35 with a 6 length win at this track over 411m. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. HEROIC FEDERER (8) is in top form lately including a dazzling win at Grafton in 19.66 two back then backing it up with a 25.29 victory at Q Lakeside over 457m latest. Must include on winning run two back. SOUL OF FIRE (5) showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 6th at Grafton in Grade 5 company. Form is hard to fault from this box, with a win and two minor placings from three starts. Has ability and can measure up. DISTANCE DRUMS (2) will be hard to beat with a drop in journey.",
